The second season of Yakusoku no Neverland. Fifteen children escape Grace Field House, a false paradise, hoping for a chance at freedom. Instead, they encounter plants and animals they have never before seen, and are chased by demons. The outside world is so beautiful, and yet is almost too cruel to face. Even so, the children refuse to give up. They are guided in their search for better lives only by a message from Minerva and a pen Norman left behind in order to fulfill their promise to return to the House to save those of their family who are still trapped within.
(Source: Aniplex of America) Note: Episode 1 streamed early on Amazon Prime on Jan 7, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on Jan 8, 2021.

LycoReco is a caf with a traditional Japanese twist located in downtown Tokyo. But the delicious coffee and sugary sweets are not the only orders this caf takes! From delivering packages short distances, to pick-ups and drop-offs on the lonely streets at night, to zombies and giant monster extermination?! Whatever your problem, we're here to help! We will solve any kind of "trouble" you may have!
Waiting for you are the ever-smiling poster-girl and the cool, serious newcomer. A petite girl who never wants to work and a young woman approaching thirty who wants to get married. And the manager is a nice guy whos obsessed with Japan!
Whatever your order is, leave it all up to us
(Source: Official Site)
Koryuu nara Sude de Taosemasu kedo, Kore tte Joushiki janain desu ka?

Fil was raised in the mountains as the grandchild of humanitys strongest sage, inheriting his talent for magic, and strong enough to defeat dragons with her bare hands.
However, one day, the great sage summoned Fil to tell him:
Fil, youre actually a girl.
"Really!? By the way, whats a girl?"
Fil's ignorance of gender and other common sense knowledge worried the great sage. Concerned about her future, he decided to enroll Fil into the Royal Academy. It will be the start of an exciting school life for the innocent strongest girl!
(Source: Piccoma, translated)
Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e Horikita
A spin-off of the Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e series. A what-if route focusing on the relationship between Kiyotaka Ayanokouji and his classmate, Suzune Horikita.
